snippet.title: New Meghan Markle bombshell claims leaves TV host feeling ‘dirty’ | Today Show Australia
snippet.description:
Subscribe 👉 https://bit.ly/2n4QLnx | Today host Karl Stefanovic has revealed he feels “dirty” after lawyers for a British newspaper publisher said on Wednesday that the Duchess of Sussex Meghan Markle crafted a letter to her estranged father so it would "pull at the heartstrings" if leaked to the public. 

(Broadcast November 11, 2021) Get more TODAY at: http://9Soci.al/KzNl50GjSJk
